message.entry: SIZE must be big enough to include all frames in I.
Parameter names must be character arrays.
Parameter ''{0}'' must be followed by a value.
Specified 'Parent' value must be a valid axes handle.
An index in INDICES cannot be less than 1 or greater than the number of frames in I.
An index in FRAMES cannot be less than 1 or greater than the number of frames in I.
An indexed image can only be uint8, uint16, double, single, or logical.
FILENAMES must be a imagedatastore, cell array of strings or character vectors.

entry.note: This is the title of a waitbar that shows up when building a montage
This will say something like _Processing 100 images_

message.entry: I should either be an MxN, MxNxP, MxNx1xP or an MxNx3xP sized array.
Montage image is a color image. DisplayRange parameter will be ignored.
Logical array mask FRAMES is larger than the number of images.
Cannot mix workspace variables with filenames.
Inputs of class dlarray are not supported.
